Package: SimRVPedigree
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Pedigrees Ascertained for a Rare Disease
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christina Nieuwoudt, Jinko Graham
Maintainer: Christina Nieuwoudt <cnieuwou@sfu.ca>
Description: Routines to simulate pedigrees ascertained for a rare disease.
    Provide functions to simulate a sample of pedigrees which have been
    ascertained according to a particular study design on the basis of
    containing multiple family members affected by a rare disease.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.5)
Imports: kinship2, dplyr(>=0.4.3)
License: What license is it under?
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: kinship2
